                                    </p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </condition>
                     
                     
                     
                     </supportDesc>
                     
                     
                     
                     <layoutDesc>
                        
                        
                        
                        <layout columns="1 " ruledLines="24" writtenLines="24">
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Uniform
                                        layout. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Hair side and flesh side of folios
                                        distinguishable. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Visible ruling by hard point,
                                        bifolium by bifolium on hair side; ruling by plummet on
                                        other side of hard point.</p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Visible quire by quire
                                        pricking, double for major lines, in outer margins only.
                                        </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Graphic filler at the end of line. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Occasional
                                        infra-linear vocalization. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Last written line within
                                        ruling. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Initial words, headings and parts of text in
                                        larger square characters. </p>
                           
                           
                           
                           <p>Marginal
                                    notes.</p>
                        
                        
                        
                        </layout>
                     
                     
                     
                     </layoutDesc>
                  
                  
                  
